<header>
  <div class="header-content">
    <div class="header-content-inner">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
          <h1 id="homeHeading">Search someone needing your help!</h1>
          <p>Find a post matching to your next visit</p>
          <div class="form-inline">
            <div class="form-group">
              <%= search_form_for @search, url: demandposts_path, method: :get do |f| %>
              <%= f.text_field :city_from, id: "city_from", class: "form-control", placeholder: "From (Option)" %>
              <%= f.text_field :city_to, id: "city_to", class: "form-control", placeholder: "To" %>

              <%= f.submit 'Search a demand', class: "btn btn-primary" %>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="bg-primary" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 text-center">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Someones want your help! Find them in COURSIER</h2>
        <hr class="light">
        <p>Can you imagine buying your favorite items if the price is doubled or trippled?
          <br/>
          The nightmare comes true if you live in oversea. Those living there will pay for it but surely it is painful. You can help them living in your next destination with some rewards!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="howto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="section-heading">How to use?</h2>
        <hr class="primary">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
        <div class="service-box">
          <i class="fa fa-4x fa-search text-primary sr-icons"></i>
          <h3>Find a demand</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Find a demand matching to your travel and contact to them.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
        <div class="service-box">
          <i class="fa fa-4x fa-suitcase text-primary sr-icons"></i>
          <h3>Buy and pack</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">You will purchase the items and pack them into your suitcase.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
        <div class="service-box">
          <i class="fa fa-4x fa-plane text-primary sr-icons"></i>
          <h3>Bring them</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Travel to your destination. Don't forget your suitcase!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
        <div class="service-box">
          <i class="fa fa-4x fa-handshake-o text-primary sr-icons"></i>
          <h3>You're done</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Exchange items with your rewards!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<aside class="bg-gray">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <div class="call-to-action">
      <h2>Take it easy. You don't have to be annoyed by your purchace in abroad!</h2>
      <hr class="light">
      <p>Buying professional items, books in your mother langage, cameras... how you get?<br>Cheese, spices, candies, rice.... you like paying double or trriple price?
      <br>Ask someone shortly visiting your town to get them!</p>
      <!--        <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path , class: "btn btn-default btn-xl sr-button" %> -->
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>

<section id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 text-center">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Contact us!</h2>
        <hr class="primary">
        <p>Ready to start your next project with us? That's great! Give us a call or send us an email and we will get back to you as soon as possible!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4 text-center">
        <i class="fa fa-envelope-o fa-3x sr-contact"></i>
        <p>
          <a href="mailto:your-email@your-domain.com">feedback@startbootstrap.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

